      "message": "Isn't it to constrained? I think we shouldn't impose such requirements on dev env, if something needs to be done outside of docker containers it should be put in prepare.yml and if that's something that doesn't fit there or can't be done there then we should find another way to write those tests.\n\nIf i had my dev env in a vm or so then configuring ssh like required by tests for this role wouldn't be a problem, but in the host OS it's unacceptable.",
